{"ID":"20260609130524-0a6ev6n","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260609130524-0a6ev6n","title":"2022年天津卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260609130622"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260609130539-0ybuetw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130539-0ybuetw","updated":"20260609130540"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在立春之日的“一片雪花”中拉开帷幕，在（   ）的早春时节挥手道别。中国“言必信，行必果”，为世界奉献了一届（   ）、安全、精彩的冬奥盛会，也让世界看到了“一个坚韧不拔、欣欣向荣的中国”。在开、闭幕式上，观众们目睹了“黄河之水天上来”的震撼场景，感受了冰雪五环“破冰”而出的唯美意境，欣赏了冰鞋划过冰面的轻盈曼妙，见证了“折柳寄情”与中央光束联动演绎的浪漫缱绻……全新科技美学与中国文化艺术的完美结合，打造出空灵而又壮观的视觉盛宴。一场冰雪运动的盛会，也是一次精神力量的（   ）：从攻克尖端技术难题的科研团队，到挥洒汗水的冬奥场馆建设者；从助力冰雪运动推广的农民滑雪队，到热情迎接四海宾朋的志愿者……无数人的默默奉献，共同成就了奥运盛事。北京冬奥会成功举办的意义，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":" "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，为动荡不安的世界带来了信心和希望。"}]},{"ID":"20260609130524-bge2841","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609130524-bge2841","updated":"20260609130601"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260609130601-tffsrki","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130601-tffsrki","updated":"20260609130601"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1．依次填入文中括号内的词语，最恰当的一组是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609130601-rsyceph","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130601-rsyceph","updated":"20260609130601"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．花团锦簇  简约  焕发                                          B．花团锦簇  简朴  勃发"}]},{"ID":"20260609130601-8smbze8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130601-8smbze8","updated":"20260609130601"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．草长莺飞  简约  勃发                                           D．草长莺飞  简朴  焕发"}]},{"ID":"20260609130601-y3xgqew","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130601-y3xgqew","updated":"20260609130601"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2．下列填入文中画线处的句子，最恰当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609130601-qjcauq5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130601-qjcauq5","updated":"20260609130601"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．不仅在于向世界发出了“一起向未来”的邀约，而且在于不断刷新纪录、超越自我"}]},{"ID":"20260609130601-r876exh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130601-r876exh","updated":"20260609130601"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．不仅在于不断刷新纪录、超越自我，而在于向世界发出了“一起向未来”的邀约"}]},{"ID":"20260609130601-webntgc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130601-webntgc","updated":"20260609130601"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．不仅在于向世界发出了“一起向未来”的邀约，而在于不断刷新纪录、超越自我"}]},{"ID":"20260609130601-y87wgrq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130601-y87wgrq","updated":"20260609130601"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．不仅在于不断刷新纪录、超越自我，而且在于向世界发出了“一起向未来”的邀约"}]},{"ID":"20260609130601-irikbmy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130601-irikbmy","updated":"20260609130601"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3．下列与文段相关的文学、文化常识，有误的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609130601-ypwju9r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130601-ypwju9r","updated":"20260609130601"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．《论语》是语录体散文，记录了孔子及其弟子的言行。“言必信，行必果”“人皆有不忍人之心”都出自《论语》。"}]},{"ID":"20260609130601-0j8oe37","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130601-0j8oe37","updated":"20260609130601"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．“欣欣向荣”语出东晋陶渊明《归去来兮辞》中的“木欣欣以向荣”。辞，古代的一种文体，一般要押韵。"}]},{"ID":"20260609130601-1xtlvc9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130601-1xtlvc9","updated":"20260609130601"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．“黄河之水天上来”与“蜀道之难，难于上青天”都使用了夸张的手法，体现了李白诗歌的浪漫主义风格。"}]},{"ID":"20260609130601-1ac83y2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130601-1ac83y2","updated":"20260609130601"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．“折柳寄情”寓含惜别怀远之意。“柳”与“留”谐音，古人离别时，有折柳枝相赠的风俗。"}]},{"ID":"20260609130524-7jplwxm","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609130524-7jplwxm","updated":"20260609130610"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260609130524-fgiexb1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130524-fgiexb1","updated":"20260609130610"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1．C    2．D    3．A"}]},{"ID":"20260609130524-ajl1rl8","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609130524-ajl1rl8","updated":"20260609130622"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260609130622-hdwz8i0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130622-hdwz8i0","updated":"20260609130622"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1．本题考查学生正确使用词语（包括熟语）的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609130622-p23z14p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130622-p23z14p","updated":"20260609130622"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"花团锦簇：形容五彩缤纷，十分鲜艳多彩的景象。草长莺飞：形容春天的景色。语境形容早春景象，应填“草长莺飞”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609130622-w5x4w86","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130622-w5x4w86","updated":"20260609130622"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"简约：指简略；不详细；简省。简朴：朴素简单。语境形容冬奥盛会的既俭省又精彩，应填“简约”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609130622-wclrai8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130622-wclrai8","updated":"20260609130622"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"焕发：光彩四射；振作。勃发：蓬勃生发；突然兴起，爆发。语境形容“精神力量”生发出来，应填“勃发”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609130622-ymran03","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130622-ymran03","updated":"20260609130622"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选C。"}]},{"ID":"20260609130622-w86mn0l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130622-w86mn0l","updated":"20260609130622"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2．本题考查学生语言表达之句子衔接的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609130622-n4lv2ui","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130622-n4lv2ui","updated":"20260609130622"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“不仅……”应搭配“而且……”，构成递进分句，排除BC；"}]},{"ID":"20260609130622-pnedct6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130622-pnedct6","updated":"20260609130622"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"从递进分句逻辑顺序看，“不断刷新纪录、超越自我”在前，“向世界发出……邀约”在后，排除A。"}]},{"ID":"20260609130622-u7g5215","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130622-u7g5215","updated":"20260609130622"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选D。"}]},{"ID":"20260609130622-e5k1ml4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130622-e5k1ml4","updated":"20260609130622"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3．本题考查学生了解并掌握常见的文学文化常识的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609130622-8ei7h2p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130622-8ei7h2p","updated":"20260609130622"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A.“都出自《论语》”错，“人皆有不忍人之心”出自《孟子》。"}]},{"ID":"20260609130622-3zfemie","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130622-3zfemie","updated":"20260609130622"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选A。"}]}]}